column5: You got my 3 today.  There's something about a guy who saves snacks in his beard that I just got to admire
Voted x2.
10 more votes
I gave you all the votes I could Brian, most everyday. While the numbers don't look good at this time Lord knows you're more than deserving of winning. Best o-luck my friend.
--you are a winner in our eyes...........  was exciting...... got to admit Brian!      Have a shockingly magical weekend all--no rain  FISH ON
To be able to get up to the position your in is amazing, as stated above you are a winner!

Thanks everyone! Still holding in 3rd, but only by about 300 votes. Things can change in a hurry so I've seen!  Let's just hope we stay in the top 10 and the judges like what they see.  http://www.wfn.tv/adopt/view.php?entry=360
New girl in first. She got about 20 votes in 30 seconds!
This will get interesting, 1st and 2nd are 3 votes apart!  and yes I'm bored and have nothing else to do.
Glad to see you stayed in 3rd, good luck!
Thanks guys! It's all up to the WFN celebrity judges now, but yes, I did manage to hold third place thanks to you folks.  Pretty amazing. I think there were almost 2,000 entries!

Folks, I have had lot's and lot's of votes and support from some great people here, but it is down to the last couple of days and I need everyone to vote each day.  There are only a small number of votes keeping me in the top 10, and I have to stay there till the contest closes for a chance!  Thanks in advance everyone!  http://www.wfn.tv/adopt/view.php?entry=360   Brian (Rattletrap2)
bump  you got my vote
ya got my vote Brian.  oh and BUMP
Thanks, Don't forget, you can have the whole family or friends vote every 24 hours!
Won't be able to vote tomorrow i don't think, I've been voting at like 11 pm and will be at my dads then, and most likely won't be able to get on the computer
Ciceri, Don't fail me now buddy! Please don't let something like family get in the way of voting!!!! LOL  J/K you have done tons! thanks
10 more

I'm still puttin in 3 a day from me...parents are not "internet" smart yet lool.  God luck man, I did the math before, if everybody could pitch in 1 vote you could win...now if they did it twice you would sweet the competion.  Good luck mate, what's the prize?

3 votes from 3 different email addy's.  Good luck!  ---  EDIT - Boy, a little shameless cheescake and beefcake there on that site. Seems to work for some people.  I'm going to toss in some more votes if I can, but it's a pretty steep drop from the top 3 to #4.

Thanks again everyone!  Some real nice comments on my contest page from some people I have a lot of respect for around here! I really appreciate that as well.  Jocko, I feel the same way about the way some people are going after votes, but hey, to each his/her own! My girls have done a wonderful thing in trying to get me in to this contest.  ONE MORE DAY!!!! We have to keep it going strong until midnight tomorrow!  http://www.wfn.tv/adopt/view.php?entry=360
For sure!  I'll throw 3 votes in again tomorrow.  Good luck!
Seems a lot of the B.A.S.S. folks are plugging for Ashlee.  I've gotten 3 e-mails in tthe past couple of days looking for votes.  Maybe the mods could send a member wide e-mail?
yeah others are using all kinds of media to get votes, I didn't think about emailing everyone in the world asking for them...LOL well in 6 hours and 41 minutes I will give my last 10 votes
Just added my last daily three votes Brian...Lots of luck...

Thanks Guys! You have all been great! I know we all have enough to do these days without trying to keep up on voting, but your efforts to do so are surely appreciated.  I could have spread the word a little better, and I know my kids and Wife have done a lot to get this out, but I really only asked for support from the folks on this board. You all are like family anyways! LOL  Even as it is, I hate to keep pestering with posts on here, but one last day!.  If I was fortunate enough to win, of course there would be a full report on here of the trip!!  Thanks again!!!
Here you go Brian.... my last 10 votes.... Good luck to ya
Hey you're in third place!  Last time I checked, I thought "I Love Me" Frank had 11,000+ votes. Now he's down to 6000-some. I must have read it wrong?
No Jocko, You read it right. He had over 12,000 votes!
I wonder what happened??? Voter fraud!?  Couldn't happen to a nicer guy!  ---  OK, I just registered another 5 votes your way.
I'm maxed out, good luck...
From the WFN Site:   With that big an "adjustment" having been made, maybe Frank might disappear from the contest altogether!
BUMP!!!!!!!  One more big push today Folks!   PLEASE VOTE!!!!!  http://www.wfn.tv/adopt/view.php?entry=360
Let's go guys, Let's keep him in 3rd.  Everyone vote tonight  VOTE HERE
